title: Old Skool Mixes Pts 1 -3 - DJ Kippax (re-up)
description:
Sorry about the lat upload. Ive just switched to a new client and i had a few problems which meant i couldnt upload. 
 Anyway here&#039;s a couple of old mixes i made years ago. Here&#039;s a brief discription of them....

Classic House Mix 1



Features tracks like S-Express - The theme, My Friend Sam - Its my pleasure, Parra Dise - Parra Dise, Tony De Bart - The real thing, Felix - Don&#039;t you want me, Prodigy - Everybody in the place, Liquid - Sweet Harmony, and more.



Classic House mix 2



Features tracks like Loveland - Let the music lift you up, Last Rhythm - Last Rhythm, Morey Kante - Yeke Yeke, Rameriaz - Habaleno, and more.



Classic House Mix 3



Features tracks like Catherine E - Im all right, Inner City - Pennies from heaven, Kathy Brown - Turn me on turn me out, Pulse - Lover that you are, Buckettheads - These sounds fall into my mind, and many more. 



For more info, bookings, and more mixes checkout www.djkippax.com

All the best
